const std::string name (  )  const

The name of this object.

When printHeader() is called, this string is prepended to the names of the data members. For example, if the prefix was set to "LPUPIL_CAMA_", then the header for the data members might be logged as LPUPIL_CAMA_X, LPUPIL_CAMA_Y etc.
